1--service.yml
  Install httpdservice on webservers nodes.
  Install mariadbservice on prodnodes.
  Make sure services are started and enabled.

2--user.yml
   create user on all managed hosts with below information.
     Use username as 'ravi'.
     Set password as 'password'.
     Password must be encrypted with Sha512.

3--file.yml
   create file ‘/root/inventoty.txt’ on all managed nodes.
     User and group ownership must be set to mark.
     Configure full permissions for user, read/write at group level and 
          no permissions for others on this file.
     Set GiD bit.
